      • onNotYetInstalled

        public void onNotYetInstalled()
        Description copied from interface: StatusCallback
        Called if Orbot is not yet installed. Usually, you handle this by checking the return value from init() on OrbotInitializer or calling isInstalled() on OrbotInitializer. However, if you have need for it, if a callback is registered before an init() call determines that Orbot is not installed, your callback will be called with onNotYetInstalled().
        Specified by:
        onNotYetInstalled in interface StatusCallback
